MODIS,or,Moderate,Resolution,Imaging,Spectroradiometer,is,a,key,data,gathering,instrument,aboard,the,Terra,and,Aqua,satellites,which,view,Earth,s,entire,surface,every,to,days,From,this,vantage,point,MODIS,generates,imagery,of,Earth,in,spectral,bands,This,imagery,is,available,for,public,purchase,online,The,MODAPS,API,allows,users,to,search,order,and,download,certain,types,of,MODIS,imagery,through,a,programmable,interface